    feat: enhance admin panel with order lifecycle, inventory tracking, and realistic demo data
    
    - Add OrderManagementPanel with full NEW→PENDING→CONFIRMED→PREPARING→READY→SERVED→COMPLETED
      workflow, role-gated status transitions, and inline item details pane
    - Extend Order model with 3 new statuses, statusLabel/statusColor helpers for consistent UI
    - Upgrade DashboardHomePanel: split into 2 stat-card rows (totals + active counts),
      add Recent Orders table, Top Products table, and Low Stock alerts list
    - Add InventoryPanel stock history tab and Restock dialog (records movement, updates stock)
    - Add InventoryMovement and AppNotification models, DAOs, and services
    - Add PermissionManager for centralised role-based access control on all modules and actions
    - Extend DashboardServiceImpl to populate status breakdowns, recent orders, top products,
      and low-stock items using the richer DashboardStats
    - Wire new services (InventoryMovementService, NotificationService) into AppContext and Main
    - Add AdminDashboard Orders panel entry in sidebar nav
    - Add upgrade_v2.sql: extends orders.status ENUM, adds inventory_movements and
      app_notifications tables, receipt_number/void_reason on payments
    - Add seed_data.sql: 20 categories, 100 products, 8 suppliers, 25 inventory items,
      10 employees, 30 customers, 36 orders across 30 days, 15 reservations, 4 notifications
    
